title: Snaps - Tennessee No. 1?, Georgia & Ohio State pull away, Ole Miss Beats Texas A&M, Michigan wins
itunes:title: Snaps - Tennessee No. 1?, Georgia & Ohio State pull away, Ole Miss Beats Texas A&M, Michigan wins
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert break down the biggest games and highlights from Week 9 of the college football season including CJ Stroud and Ohio State beating James Franklin and Penn State 44-31, Hendon Hooker and the Tennessee Volunteers dominating Kentucky 44-6, as well as Michigan and Georgia beating rivals Michigan State and Florida. #Volume #herd #colincowherd
